       IDENTIFICATION DIVISION.
       PROGRAM-ID.    COI68202.
      ******************************************************************
      *     PROGRAMA COI68202.
      *
      *     Expense Reprt - Modificaçăo, Consulta, Eliminaçăo
      ******************************************************************
      *     LOG ALTERACOES:                                            *
      *   USER     / DATA     /   REFERENCIA / OBSERVACOES             *
      *                                                                *
      *                                                                *
      ******************************************************************
       ENVIRONMENT DIVISION.
       CONFIGURATION SECTION.
       DATA DIVISION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       WORKING-STORAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                          PIC X(40) VALUE
           'INICIO WORKING-STORAGE COI68202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            DECLARACOES DE DB2
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD4805 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE COCD3401 END-EXEC.
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE SQLCA    END-EXEC.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            MENSAGEM DE INPUT E  OUTPUT
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY COCV6820.
       COPY COCV6821.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            AREAS DE TRABALHO
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       COPY VIAL0015.
       COPY VIAW0005.
       COPY VIAK0001.
       COPY VIAK0002.
       COPY COCK0001.
       COPY COCK0002.
      *
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            CONSTANTES
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-CONSTANTES.
           05 CON-COVT4805 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT4805'.
           05 CON-COVT3401 PIC X(08) VALUE 'COVT3401'.
           05 CON-01       PIC X(02) VALUE '01'.
           05 CON-SEP      PIC X(01) VALUE '-'.

       01  WS-VARIAVEIS.
           05 WS-X                 PIC 9(04) VALUE ZEROS.
           05 WS-DTMESANO          PIC X(10) VALUE SPACES.
           05 FILLER REDEFINES WS-DTMESANO.
              10 WS-DTMESANO-ANO   PIC X(04).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP1  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-MES   PIC X(02).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-SEP2  PIC X(01).
              10 WS-DTMESANO-DIA   PIC X(02).
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            PROGRAM CONTROL
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  WS-PROGRAM-CONTROL.
           05 WS-PROGNAME            PIC  X(08) VALUE 'COI68202'.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       01  FILLER                        PIC X(40) VALUE
           'FIM DA WORKING-STORAGE COI68202         '.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       LINKAGE SECTION.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *
       COPY VIAL0004.
      *
            EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0009 END-EXEC.
      *
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            0000-MAINLINE
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       0000-MAINLINE.
      *
      *    CALL 'ARREBENTA'.
      *
           PERFORM 1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
              THRU 1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
              THRU 2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.

           PERFORM 3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
              THRU 3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
      *
       0099-MAINLINE-EXIT.
           COPY VIAP0004.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '1000-INICIO-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.
      *
           MOVE VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-INPUT    TO COCV6820-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6820-ASE               TO COCV6821-ASE.
      *
       1099-INICIO-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            2000-PROC-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2000-PROC-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2000-PROC-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6820-ADE       TO COCV6821-ADE.
      *
      *--- Verifica se o periodo está aberto
      *
           MOVE COCV6820-CANO            TO COCD3401-ZANO
           MOVE COCV6820-CMES            TO COCD3401-ZMES
      *
           EXEC SQL
             SELECT CSITUER
               INTO :COCD3401-CSITUER
               FROM COVT3401_PERIODO
            WHERE ZANO     = :COCD3401-ZANO
              AND ZMES     = :COCD3401-ZMES
            FETCH FIRST ROW ONLY
           END-EXEC.

           MOVE CON-COVT3401               TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.
      *
           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.
      *
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK AND COCD3401-CSITUER = COCK0002-SITU-ABERTO
                 CONTINUE
              ELSE
                 MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO  TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                 MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO TO COCV6821-CANO-S
                 MOVE COCK0001-CPER-INV      TO COCV6821-CANO-MSG
                 MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC        TO COCV6821-CANO-CAPLIC
              END-IF
           END-IF.
      *

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              PERFORM 2100-OBTEM-DADOS
                 THRU 2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT
           END-IF

           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              MOVE 'COCV6820-ADE         '   TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-NM(1)
              MOVE  COCV6820-ADE             TO VIAL0015-CAMPO-VLR(1)
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           .
       2099-PROC-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *                   2100-OBTEM-DADOS
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       2100-OBTEM-DADOS.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '2100-OBTEM-DADOS' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6820-CFUNCIONARIO
             TO COCD4805-CIDEMP
           MOVE COCV6820-CEMPRESA
             TO COCD4805-CEMPRESA

           MOVE COCV6820-CANO
             TO WS-DTMESANO-ANO
           MOVE COCV6820-CMES
             TO WS-DTMESANO-MES
           MOVE CON-01
             TO WS-DTMESANO-DIA
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP1
           MOVE CON-SEP
             TO WS-DTMESANO-SEP2
           MOVE WS-DTMESANO
             TO COCD4805-DTMESANO

           MOVE COCV6820-SEQ
             TO COCD4805-NSEQ

           EXEC SQL
                 SELECT
                       CNUMFICH
                     , CIDEMP
                     , GNOMEEMP
                     , DTPROC
                     , DTMESANO
                     , GPAIS
                     , GEMPRESA
                     , CMOEDPAIS
                     , CIDDESP
                     , TIPODESPESA
                     , MVLR
                     , DTREG
                     , CMOED
                     , MCAMBDIA
                     , MCAMBCORR
                     , MCONTRVLR
                     , CIDCLIENTE
                     , GCLIENTE
                     , CIDPROJ
                     , GPROJ
                     , GNEGOC
                     , GOBSERV
                     , CUSERID
                     , HTIMEST
                     , CEMPRESA
                     , CPAIS
                     , NSEQ
                     , CSITU
                     , GTRAJECTO
                     , NKMS
                     , GMOTIVO
                     , CUSERAPR
                     , DDTAPR
                     , IPAYROLL
                     , NVALKMS
                 INTO
                       :COCD4805-CNUMFICH
                     , :COCD4805-CIDEMP
                     , :COCD4805-GNOMEEMP
                     , :COCD4805-DTPROC
                     , :COCD4805-DTMESANO
                     , :COCD4805-GPAIS
                     , :COCD4805-GEMPRESA
                     , :COCD4805-CMOEDPAIS
                     , :COCD4805-CIDDESP
                     , :COCD4805-TIPODESPESA
                     , :COCD4805-MVLR
                     , :COCD4805-DTREG
                     , :COCD4805-CMOED
                     , :COCD4805-MCAMBDIA
                     , :COCD4805-MCAMBCORR
                     , :COCD4805-MCONTRVLR
                     , :COCD4805-CIDCLIENTE
                     , :COCD4805-GCLIENTE
                     , :COCD4805-CIDPROJ
                     , :COCD4805-GPROJ
                     , :COCD4805-GNEGOC
                     , :COCD4805-GOBSERV
                     , :COCD4805-CUSERID
                     , :COCD4805-HTIMEST
                     , :COCD4805-CEMPRESA
                     , :COCD4805-CPAIS
                     , :COCD4805-NSEQ
                     , :COCD4805-CSITU
                     , :COCD4805-GTRAJECTO
                     , :COCD4805-NKMS
                     , :COCD4805-GMOTIVO
                     , :COCD4805-CUSERAPR
                     , :COCD4805-DDTAPR
                     , :COCD4805-IPAYROLL
                     , :COCD4805-NVALKMS
                 FROM COVT4805_EXPENSE
                 WHERE CIDEMP   = :COCD4805-CIDEMP
                 AND   CEMPRESA = :COCD4805-CEMPRESA
                 AND   DTMESANO = :COCD4805-DTMESANO
                 AND   NSEQ     = :COCD4805-NSEQ
           END-EXEC


           MOVE CON-COVT4805
             TO VIAL0002-TABLE-NAME.

           PERFORM 9020-DB2CHECK
              THRU 9029-DB2CHECK-EXIT.

      *--- Se funçăo de Eliminar e
      *--- se despesa já aprovada năo pode apagar
           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF  VIAL0001-ANULACAO
                 AND COCD4805-CUSERAPR NOT EQUAL SPACES
                     MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                       TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                     MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                       TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-S
                     MOVE COCK0001-JA-APROVADO-E
                       TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
                     MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                       TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

           IF VIAL0002-SEM-ERROS
              IF DB2-OK
                 IF VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-CFUNCIONARIO-EXISTS
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
                 ELSE
                    MOVE COCD4805-CEMPRESA  TO COCV6821-CEMPRESA
                    MOVE COCD4805-CIDEMP    TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO
                    MOVE COCD4805-DTMESANO  TO COCV6821-DTMESANO
                    MOVE COCD4805-NSEQ      TO COCV6821-SEQ
                    MOVE COCD4805-CIDPROJ   TO COCV6821-CIDPROJ
                    MOVE COCD4805-CIDDESP   TO COCV6821-CIDDESP
                    MOVE COCD4805-DTREG     TO COCV6821-DTREG
                    MOVE COCD4805-MVLR      TO COCV6821-MVLR
                    MOVE COCD4805-CMOED     TO COCV6821-CMOED
                    MOVE COCD4805-GOBSERV   TO COCV6821-GOBSERV
                    MOVE COCD4805-GTRAJECTO TO COCV6821-GTRAJECTO
                    MOVE COCD4805-NKMS      TO COCV6821-NKMS
                    MOVE COCD4805-GMOTIVO   TO COCV6821-GMOTIVO
                    MOVE COCD4805-CUSERAPR  TO COCV6821-CAPROVADO
                    MOVE COCD4805-DDTAPR    TO COCV6821-DTAPROV
                    MOVE COCD4805-CSITU     TO COCV6821-CSITDSP
                    MOVE COCD4805-MCONTRVLR TO COCV6821-CTRVLR
                    MOVE COCD4805-IPAYROLL  TO COCV6821-IPAYROLL
                    MOVE COCD4805-NVALKMS   TO COCV6821-NVALKMS

                    IF NOT VIAL0001-VISUALIZACAO
                        CONTINUE
                    END-IF
                 END-IF
              ELSE
                 IF NOT VIAL0001-CRIACAO
                    MOVE VIAK0002-ERROS-FUNCAO
                      TO VIAL0002-IND-ERROS
                    MOVE COCK0002-STATUS-ACTIVO
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-S
                    MOVE COCK0001-CFUNCIONARIO-N-EXISTS
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-MSG
                    MOVE COCK0002-CAPLIC
                      TO COCV6821-CFUNCIONARIO-CAPLIC
                 END-IF
              END-IF
           END-IF.

       2199-OBTEM-DADOS-EXIT.
           EXIT.

      *--------------------------------------------------------------
      *            3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
       3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA.
      *
           IF VIAL0001-DEBUG-SIM
              MOVE '3000-FINAL-PROGRAMA' TO VIAL0015-CALLER-ID
              PERFORM VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG
                 THRU VIAP0016-TRATA-DEBUG-EXIT
           END-IF.

           MOVE COCV6821-MSG               TO VIAL0001-MENSAGEM-OUTPUT.
           MOVE COCV6821-LENGTH            TO VIAL0001-LENGTH-MSG.
           MOVE COCV6821-NR-CAMPOS         TO VIAL0001-NR-CAMPOS.
           MOVE ZEROES
             TO VIAL0001-OCORRENCIAS.

       3099-FINAL-PROGRAMA-EXIT.
           EXIT.
      *--------------------------------------------------------------
           EXEC SQL INCLUDE VIAP0003 END-EXEC.
      *==============================================================
           COPY VIAP0016.
